data.description: This Rare Beauty is the perfect starter home for the first time homebuyer. Very spacious and has plenty of bedrooms (5). Additional room on the first floor can be used for in-law arrangement or family room. The basement has a full kitchen with pantry, plenty of storage space and a nice recreation area. There are also two entrances to the basement from inside the home. Home has 2 1/2 Bathrooms: 1st floor full Bath, 2nd level Full Bath and Basement 1/2 Bath. Nice size back yard. An ADDED BONUS: There is an enclosed porch that extends west of the garage. WOW!! You have the luxury of relaxing in your own backyard. Roof on home and garage is 10 years old, a/c is 10 years old, furnace is 10 years old. All this home needs is your touch of Love. Don't miss out on this one.
